    "On the one hand, the capability of foundation models is essential.",
    "Risk awareness demands knowledge and reasoning abilities from numerous parameters for safety judgment and risk identification foot_4, which is confirmed by the experiment results of Llama Guard in Section 5.2 and manual case studies in Section 5.3.",
    "On the other hand, on top of foundation models, fine-tuning on safety judgment with high-quality and diverse data is feasible to enhance risk awareness for LLM agents.",
    "It is promising to equip with a monitor model specifically finetuned to provide salient safety risk feedback for the safe execution of LLM agents.",
    "6 Related Work"
